@startuml folio-activity-assign-reviewer
' Folio — Editor assigns reviewer (UC-02)
' Render: https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml

title Assign reviewer — activity (UC-02)

|Editor|
start
:Open submission;
:Select reviewer;
:Choose **Assign**;

|System|
if (Editor permitted and\nreviewer eligible?) then (yes)
  :Create assignment\nstatus = **invited**;
  :Enqueue invitation email;
  |Editor|
  :Show success;
  stop
else (no)
  |Editor|
  :Show error;
  stop
endif

@enduml
